						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/12/recent-interview-voice-russia-spies-democracy-whistleblowers.html" title="14:58" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-12-07T14:58:03+00:00" pubdate>December 7, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
