                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is an inter­view I did for Voice of Rus­sia radio in Lon­don last week about spies and their rela­tion­ship with our demo­cratic pro­cesses, over­sight, Edward Snowden and much more:<br />
<iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/81265145" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
