				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/acpo" rel="tag">ACPO</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/democracy-2" rel="tag">democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/edward-snowden" rel="tag">Edward Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/infiltration" rel="tag">infiltration</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/isc" rel="tag">ISC</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/law-2" rel="tag">law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi5" rel="tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/murder" rel="tag">murder</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/npoiu" rel="tag">NPOIU</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/peter-francis" rel="tag">Peter Francis</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/police-2" rel="tag">police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/racism" rel="tag">racism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/sds" rel="tag">SDS</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/stephen-lawrence" rel="tag">Stephen Lawrence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/subversion" rel="tag">subversion</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/undercover-cops" rel="tag">undercover cops</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>			</span>
						
